Useful Content
ESP aims to provide a platform to create useful content for the
users and limit the use of the app
Useful content
: you may not share content that is offensive,
spammy or adds no value to the users on the platform,
considering the purpose of the services to predominantly provide
information in respect of load shedding and related
matters.
Advertising
: Advertising and other paid promotional material
should not exceed your independant, editorial content. We do not
allow content that conceals or misrepresents sponsored content
as independent, editorial content. Sponsorship, including, but
not limited to, ownership or affiliate interest, payment, or
material support, should be disclosed to users. The subject of
sponsored content should not focus on the sponsor without clear
disclosure.
Personal or confidential Information
: you may not add or share
any personal or confidential information of third parties
without their express consent.
Intellectual Property
: you may not infringe anyone's
intellectual property rights and must respond to clear notices
of alleged copyright infringement.
Adult content
: you may not share content that features sexual
imagery. ESP is not a platform for adult content.
Violent and other hateful content
: you may not share content
that incites or glorifies violence, any hateful or harassing
activity, including based on any of the discrimination grounds
set out in our Constitution or presents a threat to another
person or group of persons.
Although we do not have any obligation to monitor user content, we
have the right to do so and any meaningless or offensive content
as determined in our sole discretion, may be taken down without
notice and the user account may be terminated immediately and
without notice.
